    • Constructor Detail

      • Pipe

        public Pipe(java.util.List<Component> filters,
            boolean queryServiceNotFound,
            boolean queryServiceNotConnected,
            boolean containsCycle)
        Parameters:
        filters - the filter components of the pipe
        queryServiceNotFound - true if the QueryService component as the start of the pipe cannot be found, otherwise false. If true, then the filters is empty.
        queryServiceNotConnected - true if the QueryService component as the start of the pipe is connected to any filter, otherwise false. If true, then the filters is empty.
        containsCycle - true if pipe contains a cycle of filter components, otherwise false.
